Xarchiver (GTK+2 archive manager)

Xarchiver is  a lightweight desktop independent archive  manager built
with the  GTK+2  toolkit.  Xarchiver supports 7-zip, arj, bzip2, gzip,
rar, lha, lzma, lzop, deb, rpm, tar and zip archives; archive comment,
Cut/Copy/Paste/Rename, password encryption,  self-extracting binaries,
integration with Thunar file-manager and much more.

http://xarchiver.sourceforge.net